 "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2060422389142585424", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsduXgYt", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 187, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8647933, "raw_content": "", "author": "5121313", "created": 1780097119235, "profile_picture": "zPB4r5jzErAy", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "mcoulton", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsduXgYt.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/RealJamesWoods/status/2060422389142585424", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "James Woods: \"On the left is Spencer Pratt\u2019s home. On the right is Jimmy Kimmel\u2019s. Mr. Kimmel repeatedly violates FCC equal time election laws campaigning against Mr. Pratt on his late night political show. ABC\u2019s defense is that Mr. Kimmel\u2019s show is \u201ccomedy.\u201d They Are Also Selling Unicorns\"...\n", "last_comment_created": 1780121577575, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 5, "score_up": 187, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": [{"width": 959, "heightRatio": 53, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HJgXPcBboAAQLW8.jpg", "height": 512}], "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 525, "created": 1780077953000, "id": "2060422389142585424", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/796482667340382211/CoV8077b_normal.jpg", "displayName": "James Woods", "username": "RealJamesWoods"}, "content": "On the left is Spencer Pratt\u2019s home. On the right is Jimmy Kimmel\u2019s. Mr. Kimmel repeatedly violates FCC equal time election laws campaigning against Mr. Pratt on his late night political show. ABC\u2019s defense is that Mr. Kimmel\u2019s show is \u201ccomedy.\u201d \n\nThey are also selling unicorns.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 31714}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsdvfoAR", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 17, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8648857, "raw_content": "\nLast Thursday JD Vance visited Colorado Springs to address the Air Force Academy Cadets at their graduation and nothing was closed down at all. \n\nThe democrats wanted to demonstrate how valuable and important they thought they were by virtually shutting down the entire city when they arrived, like they were kings everyone had to step aside for.  They let us know they were coming by disrupting our lives and restricting our ability to travel in our own city.  The difference is stark. \n\n", "author": "Antero", "created": 1780143921817, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Colorado-Living", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "A few years ago when Biden visited Colorado Springs, they closed down Interstate 25 for hours, dividing the city in half and preventing literally tens of thoudands of people from getting to work on time.  JD Vance just came to Springs and nothing was disrupted. \n", "last_comment_created": 1780146686945, "content": "<p>Last Thursday JD Vance visited Colorado Springs to address the Air Force Academy Cadets at their graduation and nothing was closed down at all.</p>\n<p>The democrats wanted to demonstrate how valuable and important they thought they were by virtually shutting down the entire city when they arrived, like they were kings everyone had to step aside for.  They let us know they were coming by disrupting our lives and restricting our ability to travel in our own city.  The difference is stark.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 1, "score_up": 17, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2060379479021690974", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsdvdsl0", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 134, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8648142, "raw_content": "", "author": "2Scoops2Terms2Walls", "created": 1780103423949, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "EvilGreed209", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsdvdsl0.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/i/status/2060379479021690974", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Foreign workers have received 52% of American jobs since 2007. Allowing foreigners, legal or not, to access the American Dream in any significant number is a disaster. ", "last_comment_created": 1780106616114, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 3, "score_up": 134, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_